    <header>
      <div class="article-hd">
        <h1 itemprop="name" class="title">Cop Shooter Didn’t Know Michael Brown Was Robbery Suspect; Family Furious Over Report Release</h1>
        <p class="blurb">In a press conference, Ferguson Police Chief Thomas Jackson released the name of the officer who fatally shot unarmed teen Michael Brown and talked about a robbery that occurred just minutes before the shooting. Plus: Attorneys for Brown’s family release a statement about the police report.</p>
        <div class="author-info">
          
            <img src="/content/dam/theroot/80x80 author images/80x80_breanna.jpg.CROP.hd-xsmall.jpg" width="58" height="58"/>
          
          <div class="meta">

            
            <div class="byline" id="main_byline">
              <div class="auth">By: <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a rel="author" href="http://www.theroot.com/authors.breanna_edwards.html">Breanna Edwards</a></span></span></div>
            </div>
            

            <div class="date">Posted: <span itemprop="datePublished" content="2014-08-15T13:14:00.000-04:00">Aug. 15 2014 1:14 PM</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      


        <!-- Horizontal -->
        <div id="share-box-top" class="horiz-sharebox social-onload share-box-flank">
